OL,6,GThere was a little surprise for
OL,7,Gviewers during BBC Breakfast this
OL,8,Gmorning.  The regional news bulletin
OL,9,Gat 7.55am has been reinstated without
OL,10,Gmuch of a fanfare.
OL,12,FAlthough this bulletin is shorter
OL,13,Fthan the others, it effectively means
OL,14,Fthat the regional news provision
OL,15,Fduring the programme is now back to
OL,16,Fwhere it was before the pandemic.
OL,18,FThe early morning regional news
OL,19,Fservice has had something of a bumpy
OL,20,Fride over the past three years.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-
OL,4,Cpandemic schedule at breakfast
