OL,6,FIn the dark days of March 2020 it was
OL,7,Fdropped completely. Opts in the
OL,8,Fnations resumed as restrictions eased
OL,9,Fbefore early morning bulletins
OL,10,Freturned to the English regions `
OL,11,Fthough there were later occasions
OL,12,Fwhen English opts had to be dropped
OL,13,Fagain.
OL,15,FIn the English regions there have
OL,16,Falso been a number of occasions when
OL,17,Fneighbouring services have been
OL,18,Fmerged ` often though not always as a
OL,19,Fresult of Covid-related absences.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-
OL,4,Cpandemic schedule at breakfast
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
