OL,6,FBut with life now normal again, it
OL,7,Fseems right to be offering a full
OL,8,Fservice.
OL,10,FThere is an important question though
OL,11,Fabout the amount of repetition within
OL,12,Fthe bulletins. Each half-hourly
OL,13,Fbulletin can seem very similar in the
OL,14,Fabsence of a developing story.
OL,16,FIt might seem a chore to see the same
OL,17,Fthing twice. The onus should be on
OL,18,Fthe presenter and journalist
OL,19,Foutputting the opts to freshen up
OL,20,Fscripts as the morning progresses.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-
OL,4,Cpandemic schedule at breakfast
