OL,6,FIt's thought a typical Breakfast
OL,7,Fviewer sees between 30 and 40 minutes
OL,8,Fof the programme so there was a logic
OL,9,Fin dropping one of the bulletins.
OL,11,FBut on the other hand the programme's
OL,12,Faudience peaks around 8am. The loss
OL,13,Fof the 7.55am bulletin was
OL,14,Fsignificant to the nations and
OL,15,Fregions.  Hopefully the new pattern
OL,16,Fis an acceptable compromise.
OL,18,FThe regional news, weather and travel
OL,19,Fservice during Breakfast is one of
OL,20,Fthe programme's unique selling points.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-
OL,4,Cpandemic schedule at breakfast
