OL,6,FThese are not easy times for the
OL,7,FBBC's regional news teams. Last week
OL,8,Fthey went on strike over cuts to
OL,9,FEnglish local radio and action is
OL,10,Fpossible too over cuts to Radio Foyle.
OL,12,FBut hopefully the importance of
OL,13,Fregional news during BBC Breakfast is
OL,14,Fnow clearer than ever.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-
